# shadcn/ui

- Build UI with **shadcn/ui** primitives and patterns (Button, Dialog, Card, etc.), not ad-hoc styled HTML for the same role.
- If shadcn is missing from the project, run `npx shadcn@latest init`.
- Add components with `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` (e.g. `button`, `dialog`, `input`).
- Prefer composing from installed shadcn components before adding new custom component libraries.
